Hope everyone’s having a great Wednesday!

I’ve teamed up with @timepedals for another giveaway. We are giving away three sets of TIME Pedals

All you need to do: 

1.  Like the photo 
2. Tag two friends in the comments 
3. Follow @justinbarcia and @timepedals

Good luck 🍀 

We will be selecting three winners at random. The giveaway is in no way associated with Instagram. Competition closes Sunday August 1st. 

#timepedals pedalforward
